Windfall


Dependancies:

OpenGL
GLFW (makes opening opengl contexts easy)
 [needs to be compiled & installed, uses cmake to find]
GLEW (The OpenGL Extension Wrangler Library)
 [needs to be compiled & installed, uses cmake to find]
GLM (mathematics library)
 [header-only, just copied into src]


Config can be specified on the command line:
$ ./Windfall windowwidth=1024 windowheight=768 windowfullscreen=0

the following config options are available (with defaults):

windowwidth=1024
windowheight=768
windowfullscreen=0
